101101.dialog_content: If I were to engage you in combat, chief, it would be...

101102.dialog_content: Well, as it were. Victory and defeat are both common occurrences for soldiers.

101103.dialog_content: It is rare for me to get a vacation. One must enjoy it to the fullest. Engaging in a match would be a bonus.

101104.dialog_content: As both victory and defeat are possible, it is natural for one to wish for victory.

101105.dialog_content: But one never knows until one tries.

101106.dialog_content: Then—I will give the battle my all. I ask you to not hold back either, chief.

101201.dialog_content: Are you truly enjoying your vacation, chief?

101202.dialog_content: From where is this question arising?

101203.dialog_content: The boss said that even after you left on this vacation, the Quad still received comms from you.

101205.dialog_content: So the boss enjoined me to come speak with you and convince you to rest.

101206.dialog_content: You speak of Luliang? I have troubled her.

101207.dialog_content: "Mantou has dedicated all of her time and energy to Xu Heng. She so rarely gets a vacation, so you have to keep an eye on her."

101208.dialog_content: "She's not allowed to work! She has to relax and just have fun!"

101209.dialog_content: That was the boss's message to me. She expressed it many times—and thus, Miss Gengchen, you are not permitted to speak of work during this vacation!

201101.dialog_content: Goodness, what a rare sight this is. Penny for your thoughts, Director Yingzhao?

201102.dialog_content: S-Senator Hades. My apologies—I was lost in my thoughts.

201103.dialog_content: Are you thinking about work? Perhaps this is not the right setting for thoughts of that nature?

201105.dialog_content: I just—wanted to get some souvenirs from this vacation for my little sister and everyone at Tian Lu Traders.

201106.dialog_content: But the souvenir shop has so many items... It's difficult to decide what to purchase.

201107.dialog_content: Haha, I almost never see you caught in a bind, Director Yingzhao. Why don't I help you?

201108.dialog_content: Are you an expert in this area, Senator Hades?

201109.dialog_content: Not an expert, to be sure, but when it comes to picking souvenirs, I believe one should do as one pleases.

201110.dialog_content: However, I understand it is difficult for someone as conscientious as you to let go and follow your inclinations.

201111.dialog_content: That is why I offer you my assistance. I hope you will accept!

201201.dialog_content: Senator Hades is always accompanied by these two children.

201202.dialog_content: I have not interfered in the competition.

201203.dialog_content: I have not helped Lady Hades cheat, either.

201204.dialog_content: If Miss Yingzhao is not put at ease, we will begin an examination!

201205.dialog_content: Th-that is not what I meant...

201206.dialog_content: This is Leuce and this is Mintha. They're my darling little sisters. We are inseparable—where one of us goes, the others follow. As it should be.

201208.dialog_content: You have a little sister as well, no? Perhaps you'd like to spend more time with her?

201209.dialog_content: Children always grow up so quickly.

201210.dialog_content: If you miss out on all of your time with them because of work, will you not regret it?

301101.dialog_content: (Sob)... It's the witch of Omorfies... So scary...

301102.dialog_content: Little bird. What is it you were saying while sneaking about?

301104.dialog_content: It seems someone is speaking badly of Lady Hades?

301105.dialog_content: I seem to have heard them call her "scary"?

301106.dialog_content: Surely not? Our big sister would be so sad to hear that.

301108.dialog_content: Oh, no, that will not do. It seems you have the wrong impression of me, little bird.

301109.dialog_content: If we do not clear things up now, will our misunderstanding not worsen over time?

301110.dialog_content: No, I'm sorry, there's no misunderstanding. I wasn't saying anything about you, I promise—

301111.dialog_content: H-hey, let go of me! Let go of me!!

301201.dialog_content: The witch... really is even scarier than a Yaoguai.

301202.dialog_content: Speaking of which... I wonder which one of them is stronger?

301203.dialog_content: Little bird. I. Can. Hear. You.

301204.dialog_content: Miss Jinwu... called our big sister a witch?

301205.dialog_content: It's true that other people in Omorfies have called us witches...

301206.dialog_content: So where did Miss Jinwu learn this name from?

301207.dialog_content: I thought of it mys— No, wait! You misheard me!

301208.dialog_content: I never called Lady Hades a witch!

301209.dialog_content: Oh?? We misheard you, you say??

301210.dialog_content: I heard you say it as well.

301212.dialog_content: It sounds like our misunderstanding still has not been cleared up. Perhaps we should discuss it further?

401102.dialog_content: It has been many years since Ruomu Palace. So it appears it is true: No one ever steps in the same river twice, for it's not the same river and they are not the same person.

401103.dialog_content: Wahh... I still can't understand you. No wonder Master said...

401104.dialog_content: Yes? What did your master say?

401105.dialog_content: ... That you know so many things.

401106.dialog_content: If I watched your every move closely, I'd definitely learn a ton!

401109.dialog_content: Heehee. To see Gengchen's every move from up close—an opportunity like that only comes once in a lifetime!

401110.dialog_content: I won't waste it! Gengchen, you just need to keep doing what you're doing, and I'll watch!

401111.dialog_content: ...Pupil from Xihe, it seems you have only grown ever more unpredictable over the years.

401201.dialog_content: You know, Gengchen, every now and then I think, if you were here, you'd be able to defeat the Yaoguai easily, right?

401202.dialog_content: Yaoguai... I have never heard of these Visbanes before. Are they quite irksome?

401203.dialog_content: Were the trouble caused by Yaoguai to impact Xu Heng, I would be unable to merely stand to one side and observe.

401204.dialog_content: This holiday is concluded. Have you need of my company?

401205.dialog_content: No, no, the Yaoguai are my sworn enemy!

401206.dialog_content: I'm the only one allowed to defeat them! That's what I've been working toward all this time!

401208.dialog_content: If you really want to help, then train with me!

401209.dialog_content: If I can defeat you, the Yaoguai won't stand a chance against me!

401210.dialog_content: You'd be doing this to protect Xu Heng's peace! Well? Will you do it?

401211.dialog_content: ... Very well. After all, helping a pupil grow is also one of my responsibilities. But should the situation change, please notify me immediately.

501101.dialog_content: Ah, Yingzhao! Over here! I'm over here!

501102.dialog_content: It's been many years since we last met at Ruomu Palace. How astounding that you still have so much energy.

501103.dialog_content: How have you been? I understand that you have been traveling. Are you training?

501104.dialog_content: Hmph! I'll tell you, but it might scare you.

501105.dialog_content: Ever since leaving Ruomu Palace, I've been running into Yaoguai in Yu Jing!

501106.dialog_content: They've been robbing people blind out in the open and in broad daylight!

501109.dialog_content: But I defeated all of them! It was a breeze!

501110.dialog_content: If I hadn't been there, the people would have lost all their money!

501202.dialog_content: I see. This is what is called the joy of "vacation plans," is it?

501203.dialog_content: Perhaps Tian Lu Traders can invest in the entertainment sector, as there appears to be a great deal of potential here. Or...

501205.dialog_content: We're on vacation! Why are you still thinking about work, Yingzhao?

501206.dialog_content: If Linyu was here, I just know she'd say you have no work-life balance!

501207.dialog_content: Why... do you sound exactly like Lingguang right now?

501208.dialog_content: I knew I couldn't be the first person to say something like that to you. You're too serious, Yingzhao!

501209.dialog_content: You're supposed to forget about work on vacations!

601101.dialog_content: Goodness, why the long face? Do you really detest vacations that much?

601102.dialog_content: On the contrary—if one has the option of leisure time, one would naturally choose to enjoy oneself.

601103.dialog_content: However, with the present trouble in Xu Heng, my vacation here—must be delayed.

601104.dialog_content: Were I to dedicate myself solely to recreation, then...

601105.dialog_content: Haha. How dedicated you are. Such seriousness reminds me of a colleague of mine.

601106.dialog_content: Lady Hades, you should not speak poorly of Oceanus behind her back.

601107.dialog_content: Word of it may circulate and reach the wrong ears if you do.

601108.dialog_content: Who do you think that could be?

601109.dialog_content: Midsummer is short. I am simply suggesting Gengchen takes advantage of the opportunity already in front of her. Why don't you two try convincing her as well?

601202.dialog_content: You are in low spirits, indeed.

601203.dialog_content: You are Hades' servants... her sisters? Why have you come to this place?

601204.dialog_content: Ever since Lady Hades came to the seaside, she has been quite preoccupied with making mixed drinks.

601205.dialog_content: Her skills have improved very quickly, and so Lady Hades wishes to invite you to share a cup with her.

601206.dialog_content: Because she is concerned you may have difficulty relaxing.

601207.dialog_content: So will you come, Miss Gengchen?

601208.dialog_content: Hades has gone to much trouble... As I know her intentions are good, there is no reason for me to refuse.

101608901.dialog_content: In battle, there are not more than two methods of attack—the direct and the indirect; yet these two in combination give rise to an endless series of maneuvers.

101608902.dialog_content: You say... it is only a game? There is no need to be so serious?

101608903.dialog_content: My apologies. I am frequently engaged in work and have little time for recreation. I have become used to behaving in this manner.

101608904.dialog_content: Before coming here, I often heard Luliang speak of Yingzhao, saying she was "as hardworking and reliable as an AGI Mecha."

101608905.dialog_content: As I have seen, she fits this description.

101608906.dialog_content: These past few days, whenever I wished to handle Quad business, I was always stopped by Yingzhao.

101608907.dialog_content: I am also aware that she would like me to rest and relax. However...

102608701.dialog_content: The chief is an old friend of my boss, but now she wishes to engage in a match with me. Regardless of who wins or loses, I worry it will embarrass her.

102608702.dialog_content: Are you saying you will support me? Haha... I thank you. Your words remind me of a young Linyu.

102608703.dialog_content: Earlier, the chief went with me to a souvenir shop. We spent so much time there, but I could only settle upon a few items...

102608704.dialog_content: You're asking if I didn't buy enough? No, that's not it. What she said was, "Except for the ones here, pack up and ship everything to the Quad."

102608705.dialog_content: It is her vacation, but she's always finding some way to do work for the Quad. Were the boss to know, she would be so irritated...

102608706.dialog_content: What? Why can't I call her "chief"?

201608701.dialog_content: My boss and Senator Hades are entirely different people, yet somehow I always feel like they... Hm. Am I wrong?

201608702.dialog_content: In recent days, Mintha seems to have exchanged my ice water for lemonade...

201608703.dialog_content: Ah, it's not sour. She must have added honey to it. But... why would she do this?

201608704.dialog_content: Is it because we are on vacation? I do wish Senator Hades would be slightly less lax...

201608705.dialog_content: You say she is frequently like this? Ah, no—is that opinion too biased?

201608706.dialog_content: I have heard my boss once went with the chief to Omorfies. Perhaps one day, the markets of Tian Lu Traders will reach there.

202609001.dialog_content: It seems Director Yingzhao truly is an upright person. Haha. She reminds me of an old colleague.

202609002.dialog_content: You know whom I am speaking of, no?

202609003.dialog_content: I've always felt that if I were to pull a prank on Director Yingzhao, her reaction would be quite interesting.

202609004.dialog_content: (Sigh) There's no need to stop me. I'm merely thinking out loud.

202609005.dialog_content: Some time ago, I accompanied her to a souvenir shop. She cares a great deal about her little sister—it's lovely to see.

202609006.dialog_content: We just about cleared out the entire shop.

202609007.dialog_content: Leuce, Mintha, on the topic of pranking Director Yingzhao—it is not to be done again.

202609008.dialog_content: Honestly, why are you looking at me like that? Was I not the one who started it?

301609001.dialog_content: Jinwu always seems to be hiding from me. It breaks my heart to see. Why does she do it?

301609002.dialog_content: Only a few days ago, she was calling me a "witch" behind my back.

301609003.dialog_content: I never thought I would hear that name again outside of Omorfies. I can't let it stand. Where did she hear that name?

301609004.dialog_content: Oh dear, are you running away too? Are you following Jinwu's example and becoming afraid of me?

301609005.dialog_content: She seems to like Leuce and Mintha more than me. What a truly unpredictable child.

302608801.dialog_content: (Sob)... Don't give me away, please... I don't know why the witch keeps laughing. It's even scarier than when she frowns.

302608802.dialog_content: How is she always able to find me? I've been working so hard to hide...

302608803.dialog_content: Mintha and Leuce are so cute, but they never laugh! They just—

302608804.dialog_content: Keep looking at you. It makes it so hard to talk to them.

302608805.dialog_content: Ah, the witch is coming! I-I'll be on my way, then.

302608806.dialog_content: You can handle her, right? 'Cause if you can't, you should run away with me!

401608801.dialog_content: When I was on the mountain, Master was always talking about Gengchen. Is she truly as dependable in a fight as the rumors say?

401608802.dialog_content: If I want to defeat her, I'll need to catch her by surprise! Help me think up a plan!

401608803.dialog_content: Even though she has more combat experience than me, I'm not scared! Not even a little bit! Believe it!

401608804.dialog_content: To defeat the Yaoguai, I'll go train with her as soon as the competition's over!

402608901.dialog_content: In all fighting, the direct method may be used for joining battle, but indirect methods will be needed in order to secure victory. Indirect tactics, efficiently applied, are inexhaustible as heaven and earth, unending as the flow of rivers and streams.

402608902.dialog_content: If one adheres to the Art of War, one greatly increases one's chance of emerging victorious.

402608903.dialog_content: If you are interested, I can give you some of my books on the topic.

402608904.dialog_content: The handwriting and illustrations of the Prime Codex are truly outstanding, but its contents are somewhat dissimilar to the ancient tomes I read previously.

402608905.dialog_content: Hmm... What on earth does this book speak of?

402608906.dialog_content: I once met a younger Jinwu at Ruomu Palace. You are asking what sort of person she was then?

402608907.dialog_content: Hah. She was not so lively as she is now. She was, in fact, quite fearful of strangers.

501608701.dialog_content: Linyu was unable to make any friends her own age at the Quad, but Jinwu was willing to befriend her. Linyu was so grateful.

501608702.dialog_content: Ever since the battle at Ruomu Palace, there has always been one thing I could not understand:

501608703.dialog_content: When Jinwu Awakened, she was older than I was. Why does she still act like a child now?

501608704.dialog_content: I was just playing suikawari with her. Shall we go enjoy some watermelon together?

501608705.dialog_content: Jinwu is not good at drinking. As you have seen, I must bring her home so she can rest...

501608706.dialog_content: However, that drink contained no alcohol.

502608801.dialog_content: Now my opponent is Yingzhao! Wow... what a beautiful swimsuit. So mature. I want to try it on too!

502608802.dialog_content: Heehee. After we're done with the water gun fight, why don't we go play some suikawari? I'm not going to hold back, though!

502608803.dialog_content: Why am I more tired... after a water gun fight... than the Ruomu Palace battle? Is it because... it's so hot? I want an iced drink!

502608804.dialog_content: After leaving Nanjiao Isle, I thought it would be a long, long, loooooong time before I saw Yingzhao again.

502608805.dialog_content: Who would've thought it would happen so soon... Heehee. To tell you the truth, I'm really happy about it.

601609001.dialog_content: It looks like Gengchen is growing attached to Leuce and Mintha.

601609002.dialog_content: Haha, it looks like you have something you want to say. I wonder what's on your mind?

601609003.dialog_content: A few days ago, I wanted to try calling Gengchen "chief," but as soon as I did, her expression became extremely pained.

601609004.dialog_content: Haha, that makes it sound like I have bad intentions, no?

601609005.dialog_content: Back when Gengchen was on her own, she always had a great deal on her mind. It seemed like the weight of the world was on her shoulders.

601609006.dialog_content: I have heard of the business in Xu Heng as well. I hope that, well, how would you say it... I hope she is able to relax during her vacation.

601609007.dialog_content: After the competition is over, we should do a girls' night out.

601609008.dialog_content: Oh, do you want to come too, Admin? It'll be a night you won't forget.

602608901.dialog_content: The onset of troops is like the rush of a torrent which will even roll stones along in its course. The quality of decision is like the well-timed swoop of a falcon which enables it to strike and destroy its victim.

602608902.dialog_content: As it is a vacation, Lady Hades has no need to constrain herself to the rules of Xu Heng.

602608903.dialog_content: There is no need to use the title of "chief." You and I may do as we wish.

602608904.dialog_content: Are Leuce and Mintha Lady Hades' Access Keys, or her sisters? Or perhaps they are both?

602608905.dialog_content: A long, long time ago, the Quad deputy and I paid a visit to Omorfies.

602608906.dialog_content: It was quite a lovely place. Only, its food was... somewhat plain.
